Runtime Security (optional / bonus)

 Falco (runtime threat detection)

Falco watches system calls and alerts on suspicious behavior (exec in container, unexpected network connections).

Install Falco via Helm in cluster (example):

helm repo add falcosecurity https://falcosecurity.github.io/charts
helm repo update
helm install falco falcosecurity/falco --namespace falco --create-namespace


Add rules tuned to your app (e.g., detect shell exec in app container). Configure alert sinks (Slack, PagerDuty).
